  "title": "Florist  | Up to $2.8K | 5.5 Days | Bishan - 0310",
  "description": "<p><strong>Florist </strong></p><ul><li>Location: Midview City (Bishan)</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 Day work week (Off day on a weekday)</li><li>Full Work Day (Including Sundays): 8.30am - 5.30pm</li><li>Saturdays: 9.00am to 1.00pm OR 12.00pm - 4.00pm</li><li>Salary: $1800 - $2800 [ Depends on Experience ]</li><li>1 to 2 years of relevant experience in making hand bouquets, floral arrangement and hamper packing</li><li>Preferably with professional flower arrangement / design certification</li></ul><p>Interested applicants can also send your resume to (Liwenpoh741#gmail.com) and allow our consultant to match you with our clients. No Charges will be incurred by Candidates for any service rendered.</p><p>WA ME <a href=\"tel:9735 4019\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>9735 4019</strong></a> for more Florist role</p><p><u>Responsibilities</u></p><ul><li>Processing of daily customer's orders (i.e. Grand opening stands, hampers for various occasions, condolence wreaths, hand bouquets, etc.)</li><li>Assisting in the daily preparation works (i.e. flowers picking and arrangement, sponges soaking, stock-taking, etc.)</li><li>Undertake other duties as assigned by the Manager</li></ul><p>POH LI WEN REG NO: R25136683</p><p>THE SUPREMEHR ADVISORY PTE LTD EA NO: 14C7279</p>",
